Refer to the DeepStream SDK documentation for a description of the "nvdsudpsrc"
and "nvdsudpsink" components.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pre-requisites:
- GStreamer-1.0 Development package
- GStreamer-1.0 Base Plugins Development package
- CUDA Runtime 12.0+
- Rivermax SDK

Install gstreamer developement packages using:
   sudo apt-get install libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev libgstreamer1.0-dev

Rivermax SDK:
   Follow the instructions at https://developer.nvidia.com/networking/rivermax-getting-started to install the Rivermax SDK.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compiling and installing the plugin:
Export or set in Makefile the appropriate CUDA_VER
Run make and sudo make install

NOTE: To compile the sources, run make with "sudo" or root permission.









